    "references": {
      "sha256": "4bb4539d859d9861fae85d7aecd78d1dcaed0bc0eafe513ebf6889f56247f83e",
      "source_region": "div.problem-additional-text",
      "text": "[Er48] Erd\\H{o}s, P., On arithmetical properties of Lambert series. J. Indian Math. Soc. (N.S.) (1948), 63-66."
    },
    "remarks": {
      "sha256": "6069e0448cbff8abd65262f5c1698bec9c2b3c42bb558513dca19edb523fbf06",
      "source_region": "div.problem-additional-text",
      "text": "A conjecture of Chowla. Erd\\H{o}s \\cite{Er48} proved that this is true if $t\\geq 2$ is an integer."
    },
    "statement": {
      "sha256": "ff2302dcaf6998040d3429962d31436b2e21a4407176b900e67ce3673d1050cf",
      "source_region": "div#content",
      "text": "Let $t>1$ be a rational number. Is\\[\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty\\frac{1}{t^n-1}=\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty \\frac{\\tau(n)}{t^n}\\]irrational, where $\\tau(n)$ counts the divisors of $n$?"
    }
  },
